com.stefanski.booksearch.managers

Class WebLinkManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stefanski.booksearch.managers.WebLinkManager

  • public class WebLinkManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to create new web link instances like initial web link or web link.

    WebLinkManager is following the Singleton Pattern:
  • Only one object is created and no more.
  • Global point of access via getInstance().

Author:
Frederik Stefanski
